g.text: selects option to record the administration of a vaccine to a SNS User
presses the "Press Here To See The User's Data" button
verifies if user is in waiting room
requests name and age of the user
shows the user´s name and age
presses the "Press Here To Confirm" button
verifies if user is in waiting room
sends snsUserNumber and vaccineType for storage
opens new JavaFX window and switches to "RecordAdministrationVaccineToUserController2"
requests the vaccine that the user has taken and its lot number
presses the "Press Here To Confirm" button
gets the correct vaccine dose number
sends vaccineLotNumberFinal, currentVaccine and vaccineDoseNumber for storage
requests the creation of a new Vaccination Event
gets all the data and makes a VaccinationEvent and adds it to vaccinationEventList
starts 30 minute timer to inform the user when he can leave the "RecoveryRoom"
sends message to user to inform he can leave the "RecoveryRoom"
